dies that eradicate the illness altogether.\r\n\r\nDr Khedekar feels that the focus of research in medical science should now be about  genome and protein .\r\n<h2>What homeopathy costs?</h2>\r\nYour first consultation with a private homeopath will usually cost between INR 500 to INR 10,000. Further appointments usually cost less – about INR 500 to INR 5000 depending on the location of the place and experience of homeopath. It will also depend on the skill level of his staff or assistants who usually take the first case and prepare it for the main consultant.\r\n\r\nYour remedy will usually be included in the consultation price, but do check this first. Homeopathic tablets or other products usually cost around INR 100 to INR500 if you need to buy them separately in India.\r\n\r\nSo it is a very exciting area in which Dr Khedekar has started working !', 'What the masters say about Dr. Shreepad Khedekar', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '66-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-08-11 09:50:13', '2017-08-11 09:50:13', '', 66, 'http://eheilung.com/ehblog/?p=67', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2017-08-11 09:51:06', '2017-08-11 09:51:06', 'Dr. Shreepad Khedekar, B.H.M.S, MD, over past decade has been creating milestones in the field of Science and Medicine. He has established his name in doing what was imagined to be impossible, curing patients with Autism, Cancers, Motor Neurone Diseases and the so called ''chronic incurable diseases.\r\n\r\nThis award recognizes Dr. Shreepad Khedekar as one of the young and dynamic doctors who has achieved a lot of recognition and credit through his in-depth study and research in various fields from homeopathy, autism in children, alopecia and other chronic diseases.\r\n\r\nAt the event, U.S. Consul General, His Excellency Mr. Peter Haas honored various organizations that have excelled in the field of Information Technology, Media &amp; Entertainment, Banking and Finance and for their colossal contribution towards strengthening Indo-US ties through their business. The objective of the awards is aimed at recognizing corporates and entrepreneurs who have showcased exemplary and outstanding performance in varied dimensions of Indian and US businesses. He titled Dr. Shreepad Khedekar as the ''<strong>Best living Homeopath in the world today''</strong>.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2507" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2507" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Image-4-2-300x223.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="223" /> US consul General, His Excellency Peter Haas giving the award of OutStanding Achiever to Dr. Shreepad Khedekar[/caption]\r\n\r\nThe awards were announced at a formal presentation ceremony in Mumbai on April 29, 2013. US Consul General, H. E. Mr. Peter Haas, presented the awards to the winning organizations.\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/wETw5Tm9gWE\r\n\r\nOn receiving the award, Dr. Shreepad Khedekar, Clinical Director, Imperial Clinic, <strong>"Winning this award is a testimony to my continuous commitment and dedication in the research and development in the study related to homeopathy and other therapies related. I am honored to have received the award from the US Consul General and feel completely gratified to have been awarded with other eminent personalities in the field of science. But what amazes me the most is to have received this award from the American Con. General for a German Science that I studied in India and teach in Europe"</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>About Dr. Shreepad Khedekar</strong>\r\n\r\nDr. Shreepad Khedekar, B.H.M.S, MD, Clinical Director at Imperial Clinics which a specialty cure clinic in Mumbai, Goa and Belgrade, Over past decade he has been writing books, developing softwares for budding doctors, teaching, researching and treating patients with severe chronic conditions. Dr .Khedekar has established his name in doing what was imagined to be impossible, curing patients with Stage 1 Cancers, Motor Neurone Diseases, skin ailments, etc.\r\n<h2>What homeopathy costs?</h2>\r\nYour first consultation with a private homeopath will usually cost between INR 500 to INR 10,000. Further appointments usually cost less – about INR 500 to INR 5000 depending on the location of the place and experience of homeopath. It will also depend on the skill level of his staff or assistants who usually take the first case and prepare it for the main consultant.\r\n\r\nYour remedy will usually be included in the consultation price, but do check this first. Homeopathic tablets or other products usually cost around INR 100 to INR500 if you need to buy them separately in India.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2341" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2341" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DR.-KHEDEKAR.-KHEDEKAR-300x167.png" alt="" width="300" height="167" /> Imperial clinics Mumbai[/caption]\r\n\r\n<b><a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar, BHMS, MD</a> (homeopathy), a specialist for over 17 years, he has used homeopathy in his Switzerland, Belgrade and Mumbai practice for the last 17 years. He lectures in homeopathy at Switzerland, Croatia and at the Serbian Doctors Association (SLD) Teaching Centre in Belgrade and has a busy private practice in Dadar, Mumbai and at Shushrusha Citizens co-operative hospital, Mumbai and is the only Homeopath in their 60 year history.</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Dr. <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Shreepad</a> <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Khedekar</a>  is the Clinical Director, Imperial clinics Mumbai and Imperial clinics Belgrade, Consultant at Shushrusha Citizens Co-op Hospital Mumbai and Physician to several international stars and celebrities.</b>\r\n\r\nPlease do take a look at his CV: <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'US Consul General titles Dr. Shreepad Khedekar as the Best Homeopath in the world', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'us-consul-general-titles-dr-shreepad-khedekar-as-the-best-homeopath-in-the-world', '', '', '2017-08-11 09:51:15', '2017-08-11 09:51:15', '', 0, 'http://eheilung.com/ehblog/?p=68', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(69, 1, '2017-08-11 09:51:06', '2017-08-11 09:51:06', 'Dr. Shreepad Khedekar, B.H.M.S, MD, over past decade has been creating milestones in the field of Science and Medicine. He has established his name in doing what was imagined to be impossible, curing patients with Autism, Cancers, Motor Neurone Diseases and the so called ''chronic incurable diseases.\r\n\r\nThis award recognizes Dr. Shreepad Khedekar as one of the young and dynamic doctors who has achieved a lot of recognition and credit through his in-depth study and research in various fields from homeopathy, autism in children, alopecia and other chronic diseases.\r\n\r\nAt the event, U.S. Consul General, His Excellency Mr. Peter Haas honored various organizations that have excelled in the field of Information Technology, Media &amp; Entertainment, Banking and Finance and for their colossal contribution towards strengthening Indo-US ties through their business. The objective of the awards is aimed at recognizing corporates and entrepreneurs who have showcased exemplary and outstanding performance in varied dimensions of Indian and US businesses. He titled Dr. Shreepad Khedekar as the ''<strong>Best living Homeopath in the world today''</strong>.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2507" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2507" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Image-4-2-300x223.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="223" /> US consul General, His Excellency Peter Haas giving the award of OutStanding Achiever to Dr. Shreepad Khedekar[/caption]\r\n\r\nThe awards were announced at a formal presentation ceremony in Mumbai on April 29, 2013. US Consul General, H. E. Mr. Peter Haas, presented the awards to the winning organizations.\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/wETw5Tm9gWE\r\n\r\nOn receiving the award, Dr. Shreepad Khedekar, Clinical Director, Imperial Clinic, <strong>"Winning this award is a testimony to my continuous commitment and dedication in the research and development in