(76, 1, '2017-08-11 09:55:19', '2017-08-11 09:55:19', '<h2 class="strakline">When it comes to autism, the focus of homeopathy is to treat the child as a whole and not just the symptoms says Dr Shreepad Khedekar MD (hom) for autism treatment in homeopathy and autism recovery in homeopathy.</h2>\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mrpz7rQZuk8&t=4s\r\n<div class="edi-date fl eventtracker" data-event-sub-cat="Author" data-event-title="yes"><span class="edi-date fl"><a href="http://www.thehealthsite.com/author/sandhya-raghavan/">by Sandhya Raghavan  </a></span></div>\r\n<div class="fr art-del-sc">\r\n<div class="clear">\r\n\r\nImagine your child smothering you in hugs and kisses when you come back home after work. Truly priceless.  But did you know that many parents in the world are denied of this simple yet beautiful pleasure because their children fail to acknowledge their presence? It’s not because these children are antisocial, it’s because they have autism, a developmental disability that afflicts one in every thousand children, taking away their ability to communicate and forge relationships with others using language. Read: 5 shocking things that can increase the risk of autism in children.\r\n\r\nConvention treatment for autism leaves a lot to be desired since it only focuses on treating the symptoms of the disorder and not the child. The world is now slowly waking up to the powers of alternative medicines especially when it comes to treating disorders on the autistic spectrum. One such discipline that has seen brilliant results in not only treating but also reversing autism is homoeopathy.\r\n\r\nOn April 10, World Homeopathy Day, we spoke to renowned homoeopath Dr Shreepad Khedekar from Imperial Clinics about his take on autism and how homoeopathy works towards stimulating the child’s DNA to correct the disorder, helping him or her cure autism rather than learning how to function around it. Dr Khedekar is an authority in the field of paediatric developmental disorder management, and he has initiated a seven-year-old international study involving children with issues such as delayed development, autism, tuberous sclerosis, dyspraxia, borderline Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD) and cerebral palsy. Autism treatment in homeopathy, Autism recovery homeopathy how is that possible? How is ADHD homeopathic treatment done, will homeopathy for ADHD work?\r\n\r\n<strong>What is wrong with conventional treatment methods?</strong>\r\n\r\n“In autism, there is a complete breakdown in coordination between mental activities,” says Dr Khedekar. “In the conventional system of medicine, the treatment for autism is not the best; it, in fact, is very suppressive in nature. Remedies are given to suppress the hyperactivity of child can be suppressed, or they try to take care of the secondary effects of autism, like its complications. The answer to curing rather than just managing autism lies in the DNA of the child according to Dr Khedekar. “The repair has to be done at the level of the child’s DNA. Only then can you bring it out of autism. This is what I call the genetic repair process. Through homoeopathy, we stimulate the child’s own repair mechanism,” he adds. The focus of the treatment and management through homoeopathy is not to treat the isolated symptoms of the developmental disorder, but to treat the child as a whole and help in building up the personality traits of the child from the time of the treatment.\r\n\r\n<strong>What causes autism according to homoeopathy?</strong>\r\n\r\nDr Khedekar says that it is difficult to pinpoint exact causes of autism. But in his experience, he has come across certain factors that were common in most of the cases.\r\n\r\n•    Stress during pregnancy- Dr Khedekar says, “50% of the time, stress during pregnancy is a positive finding. Mother’s mental health during the time of pregnancy can impact the development of the child. “In most cases, the mother was going through stress during pregnancy such problems with the husband or the in-laws,” recounts Dr Khedekar.\r\n\r\n•    Mercurial compounds in vaccines – “Some newly introduced vaccines can be a trigger for autism mainly due to their mercurial compounds,” states Dr Khedekar. “Although there are no studies to support this, I have found this to be a trigger in my experience.”\r\n\r\n<strong>What are the signs of autism in children?</strong>\r\n\r\nDr Khedekar says that the initial symptoms of the disorder start showing at two years of age. Following are some of the most conspicuous symptoms of the disorder.\r\n\r\n•    Lack of eye contact in the child\r\n\r\n•    No separation anxiety is seen in the child on being taken away from its parents\r\n\r\n•    No emotional attachment towards parents or caregivers\r\n\r\n•    Prefers to stay alone and play solitary games\r\n\r\n•    Does not make friends\r\n\r\n•    Impaired verbal skills. Cannot make full sentences\r\n\r\n•    Repetitive activities like pinching oneself, banging head, rubbing genitals\r\n\r\n•    Attachment towards inanimate objects like toys\r\n\r\nAlthough the symptoms start showing only after two years, the actual damage happens when the child is in the womb. “When the mother is going through stress, the child, even in utero, uses its intelligence to fend off the effects of the adverse conditions in its mother’s womb,” he says. This is when the developmental disorder starts taking shape.\r\n\r\n<strong>How does homoeopathy treat autism?</strong>\r\n\r\n•    Good behaviour therapy – The child has to be left in the care of a therapist who can mould the child’s behaviour. This will bring out a positive change in the child who will be taught basic skills like looking, listening, reading, conversing and mimicking.\r\n\r\n•    A good diet – In Dr Khedekar’s experience with autistic children, he has found that most have some sensitivity to proteins such as casein (found commonly in milk) and gluten. “A diet free of these two can go a long way in helping the child fight autism,” he emphasises.\r\n\r\n•      A good homoeopathic remedy- Finally, formulating the right homoeopathic remedy is the last step in curing the child. For this, prescriptions should be made through observations. The child has to be understood as a whole and not just as a clutch of symptoms. So understanding the child’s mind and body is important in curing autism.\r\n\r\n<strong>How homoeopathy works</strong>\r\n\r\nTo formulate a similimum or a cure, a homoeopath has to observe the child acutely for its behaviour and preferences. “The doctor makes a note of the child’s behaviour, whether it is screaming, shouting, crawling or performing repetitive behaviours. He will also observe whether the child prefers warmer or cooler temperatures or sweet or sour foods,” the doctor states. This, according to Dr Khedekar, gives the homoeopath insights into the child’s genetic makeup, which will in turn help in formulating the right homoeopathic remedy. Once the remedy is administered, the genetic reversal is triggered and the child is cured.\r\n\r\n<strong>Way forward</strong>\r\n\r\nSceptics should know that autistic children treated with homoeopathy were monitored by Dr Khedekar in a seven-year-long study. Pre and post-treatment observations have found that 80 percent of these children are living physically and psychologically balanced lives! Even when convention medicine gropes in the dark looking for answers, homoeopathy has proved that a seemingly complex disorder like autism can be reversed with simple and holistic steps.\r\n\r\n<em>Dr Shreepad Khedekar has treated world famous <strong>Tennis Star Novak Djokovic </strong>for asthma. Has also cured many European football stars playing the European Premier League. Has his own practice in Europe and believes in research, has submitted hundreds of case studies to medical journals internationally. He is a physician, teacher, researcher, and author. He has written four books on Homeopathy. He operates through his clinics in Dadar and Belgrade and is also a consultant at Shushrusha Hospital, Mumbai.</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>For more details: www.imperialclinics.com</em></strong>\r\n<h2>What homeopathy costs?</h2>\r\nYour first consultation with a private homeopath will usually cost between INR 500 to INR 10,000. Further appointments usually cost less – about INR 500 to INR 5000 depending on the location of the place and experience of homeopath. It will also depend on the skill level of his staff or assistants who usually take the first case and prepare it for the main consultant.\r\n\r\nYour remedy will usually be included in the consultation price, but do check this first. Homeopathic tablets or other products usually cost around INR 100 to INR500 if you need to buy them separately in India.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2341" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2341" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DR.-KHEDEKAR.-KHEDEKAR-300x167.png" alt="" width="300" height="167" /> Imperial clinics Mumbai[/caption]\r\n\r\n<b><a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar, BHMS, MD</a> (homeopathy), a specialist for over 17 years, he has used homeopathy in his Switzerland, Belgrade and Mumbai practice for the last 17 years. He lectures in homeopathy at Switzerland, Croatia and at the Serbian Doctors Association (SLD) Teaching Centre in Belgrade and has a busy private practice in Dadar, Mumbai and at Shushrusha Citizens co-operative hospital, Mumbai and is the only Homeopath in their 60 year history.</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Dr. <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Shreepad</a> <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Khedekar</a>  is the Clinical Director, Imperial clinics Mumbai and Imperial clinics Belgrade, Consultant at Shushrusha Citizens Co-op Hospital Mumbai and Physician to several international stars and celebrities.</b>\r\n\r\nPlease do take a look at his CV: <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'World Homeopathy Awareness Week: Can homeopathy treat Autism and ADHD?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '74-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-08-11 09:55:19', '2017-08-11 09:55:19', '', 74, 'http://eheilung.com/ehblog/?p=76', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(77, 1, '2017-08-11 09:56:12', '2017-08-11 09:56:12', '<strong>Dr Shreepad Khedekar explains how homeopathy can stimulate the body to deal with Alzheimer''s disease.</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2694" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/alzheimer-300x196.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="196" />\r\n\r\nWhen an elderly Kathak exponent from Kolkata started forgetting her dance steps midway during her performance, little did she know that Alzheimer’s was staking a claim on her memories. An 80-year-old gentleman found himself in a similar predicament when he couldn’t recollect the address of the house he had lived for forty years of his life.\r\nBut instead of giving into the progressive ailment, they both sought out answers to their problem in holistic medicine, and this brought them to Dr Shreepad Khedekar, an exponent in homeopathic medicines and MD of Imperial Clinics, who has treated the likes of tennis player Novak Djokovic and Serbian footballer Marko Pantelic.\r\nLong story short, the 70-year-old dancer is back on stage, pursuing her vocation with renewed vigour, and the gentleman, who started responding positively to the medication within just two months, has shown remarkable progress after three years on homeopathic medication.\r\nIn the winter of your life, you find solace in the memories that made your life sweeter. In these ‘Golden Years’, many elderly people with Alzheimer’s wage a losing battle against their own body in a bid to preserve their sanity. Eventually, Alzheimer’s leaves them with no choice but to concede defeat.\r\n\r\n<strong>Who is at risk?</strong>\r\n• Those with a rare gene mutation – Dr Khedekar says, “The risk of developing Alzheimer’s is higher if a first-degree relative, like parents or siblings, have it. People with rare gene mutation Apolipoprotein E4 (APoE4) is linked to early-onset Alzheimer’s symptoms as early as their 30s.”\r\n• The elderly – “Increasing age is the greatest known risk factor for Alzheimer’s. The ailment is not a part of normal ageing, but its risk increases significantly after the age of 65. The risk doubles every decade after age 60,” says the doctor.\r\n• More women than men – Dr Khedekar says that more females than males are at greater risk, attributed to the fact that women live longer than men. “Women carrying a copy of APoE4 gene are more likely to develop Alzheimer’s as compared to men may be due to gene interaction with oestrogen,” adds the doctor.\r\n• Head traumas and strokes – “Physical trauma as in accident where the brain suffers significant damage, or medical conditions like stroke or lack of oxygen can predispose one to Alzheimer’s,” states Dr Khedekar.\r\nWhat are the limitations of conventional treatment for Alzheimer’s?\r\nDr Khedekar says that allopathy has very less to offer for the treatment of Alzheimer’s. “Considering that it only has palliative drugs like Tacrine, Rivastigmine, Galantamine, Donepezil and Memantine which work as Acetylcholinesterase inhibitors, allopathy only has marginal benefits and that too with many side effects.” In stark contrast with this is homeopathy, which treats the sufferer at a holistic level and helps the sufferer’s body correct the pathology on its own accord, without ANY side effects.\r\n“If diagnosed early, homeopathic remedies can help in significantly arresting or even possibly reversing the disease,” says the doctor. Some of the remedies used for treating Alzheimer’s are:\r\n• Gelsemium\r\n• Nux Vomica\r\n• Mercurius\r\n• Baryta Carbonica\r\n• Conium\r\n• Lycopodium\r\n• Alumina\r\n• Natrum Sulphur\r\nHow can one reduce the risk of Alzheimer’s?\r\n• Mind -The key to reducing Alzheimer’s risk according to Dr Khedekar is to keep the mind occupied and active. “Mentally stimulating activities like learning a new language or playing puzzles, games and solving problems can prevent brain atrophy,” he states. “Music therapy has also helped to a large extent.”\r\n• Body- It goes without saying that a healthy lifestyle goes a long way in preventing any degenerative disease. “Cardiovascular exercising can help. A healthy diet, social engagement and intellectual stimulation are known to reduce risk factors for Alzheimer’s,” says Dr Khedekar.\r\nHow can caregivers help, in addition to homeopathic treatment?\r\nCaring for someone with Alzheimer’s can be demanding; suddenly, someone whom you have known all your life behaves abnormally, displays aggression or wanders far away from home. “Memory and language loss, impaired judgment, and other cognitive changes caused by Alzheimer’s can also complicate treatment for other health conditions; therefore caregiver may have to cope with a lot of mental and physical challenges,” adds Dr Khedekar. “Becoming well-informed about the disease is one important long-term strategy.”\r\nApart from this, the doctor prescribes good coping skills, a strong support network and respite care to help caregivers handle the stress of caring for a loved one with Alzheimer’s disease.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2507" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2507" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Image-4-2-300x223.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="223" /> US consul General, His Excellency Peter Haas giving the award of OutStanding Achiever to Dr. Shreepad Khedekar[/caption]\r\n<h2>What homeopathy costs?</h2>\r\nYour first consultation with a private homeopath will usually cost between INR 500 to INR 10,000. Further appointments usually cost less – about INR 500 to INR 5000 depending on the location of the place and experience of homeopath. It will also depend on the skill level of his staff or assistants who usually take the first case and prepare it for the main consultant.\r\n\r\nYour remedy will usually be included in the consultation price, but do check this first. Homeopathic tablets or other products usually cost around INR 100 to INR500 if you need to buy them separately in India.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2341" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2341" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DR.-KHEDEKAR.-KHEDEKAR-300x167.png" alt="" width="300" height="167" /> Imperial clinics Mumbai[/caption]\r\n\r\n<b><a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar, BHMS, MD</a> (homeopathy), a specialist for over 17 years, he has used homeopathy in his Switzerland, Belgrade and Mumbai practice for the last 17 years. He lectures in homeopathy at Switzerland, Croatia and at the Serbian Doctors Association (SLD) Teaching Centre in Belgrade and has a busy private practice in Dadar, Mumbai and at Shushrusha Citizens co-operative hospital, Mumbai and is the only Homeopath in their 60 year history.</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Dr. <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Shreepad</a> <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Khedekar</a>  is the Clinical Director, Imperial clinics Mumbai and Imperial clinics Belgrade, Consultant at Shushrusha Citizens Co-op Hospital Mumbai and Physician to several international stars and celebrities.</b>\r\n\r\nPlease do take a look at his CV: <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Can homeopathy help those with Alzheimer’s Disease?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'can-homeopathy-help-those-with-alzheimers-disease', '', '', '2017-08-11 09:56:12', '2017-08-11 09:56:12', '', 0, 'http://eheilung.com/ehblog/?p=77', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(78, 1, '2017-08-11 09:56:12', '2017-08-11 09:56:12', '<strong>Dr Shreepad Khedekar explains how homeopathy can stimulate the body to deal with Alzheimer''s disease.</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2694" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/alzheimer-300x196.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="196" />\r\n\r\nWhen an elderly Kathak exponent from Kolkata started forgetting her dance steps midway during her performance, little did she know that Alzheimer’s was staking a claim on her memories. An 80-year-old gentleman found himself in a similar predicament when he couldn’t recollect the address of the house he had lived for forty years of his life.\r\nBut instead of giving into the progressive ailment, they both sought out answers to their problem in holistic medicine, and this brought them to Dr Shreepad Khedekar, an exponent in homeopathic medicines and MD of Imperial Clinics, who has treated the likes of tennis player Novak Djokovic and Serbian footballer Marko Pantelic.\r\nLong story short, the 70-year-old dancer is back on stage, pursuing her vocation with renewed vigour, and the gentleman, who started responding positively to the medication within just two months, has shown remarkable progress after three years on homeopathic medication.\r\nIn the winter of your life, you find solace in the memories that made your life sweeter. In these ‘Golden Years’, many elderly people with Alzheimer’s wage a losing battle against their own body in a bid to preserve their sanity. Eventually, Alzheimer’s leaves them with no choice but to concede defeat.\r\n\r\n<strong>Who is at risk?</strong>\r\n• Those with a rare gene mutation – Dr Khedekar says, “The risk of developing Alzheimer’s is higher if a first-degree relative, like parents or siblings, have it. People with rare gene mutation Apolipoprotein E4 (APoE4) is linked to early-onset Alzheimer’s symptoms as early as their 30s.”\r\n• The elderly – “Increasing age is the greatest known risk factor for Alzheimer’s. The ailment is not a part of normal ageing, but its risk increases significantly after the age of 65. The risk doubles every decade after age 60,” says the doctor.\r\n• More women than men – Dr Khedekar says that more females than males are at greater risk, attributed to the fact that women live longer than men. “Women carrying a copy of APoE4 gene are more likely to develop Alzheimer’s as compared to men may be due to gene interaction with oestrogen,” adds the doctor.\r\n• Head traumas and strokes – “Physical trauma as in accident where the brain suffers significant damage, or medical conditions like stroke or lack of oxygen can predispose one to Alzheimer’s,” states Dr Khedekar.\r\nWhat are the limitations of conventional treatment for Alzheimer’s?\r\nDr Khedekar says that allopathy has very less to offer for the treatment of Alzheimer’s. “Considering that it only has palliative drugs like Tacrine, Rivastigmine, Galantamine, Donepezil and Memantine which work as Acetylcholinesterase inhibitors, allopathy only has marginal benefits and that too with many side effects.” In stark contrast with this is homeopathy, which treats the sufferer at a holistic level and helps the sufferer’s body correct the pathology on its own accord, without ANY side effects.\r\n“If diagnosed early, homeopathic remedies can help in significantly arresting or even possibly reversing the disease,” says the doctor. Some of the remedies used for treating Alzheimer’s are:\r\n• Gelsemium\r\n• Nux Vomica\r\n• Mercurius\r\n• Baryta Carbonica\r\n• Conium\r\n• Lycopodium\r\n• Alumina\r\n• Natrum Sulphur\r\nHow can one reduce the risk of Alzheimer’s?\r\n• Mind -The key to reducing Alzheimer’s risk according to Dr Khedekar is to keep the mind occupied and active. “Mentally stimulating activities like learning a new language or playing puzzles, games and solving problems can prevent brain atrophy,” he states. “Music therapy has also helped to a large extent.”\r\n• Body- It goes without saying that a healthy lifestyle goes a long way in preventing any degenerative disease. “Cardiovascular exercising can help. A healthy diet, social engagement and intellectual stimulation are known to reduce risk factors for Alzheimer’s,” says Dr Khedekar.\r\nHow can caregivers help, in addition to homeopathic treatment?\r\nCaring for someone with Alzheimer’s can be demanding; suddenly, someone whom you have known all your life behaves abnormally, displays aggression or wanders far away from home. “Memory and language loss, impaired judgment, and other cognitive changes caused by Alzheimer’s can also complicate treatment for other health conditions; therefore caregiver may have to cope with a lot of mental and physical challenges,” adds Dr Khedekar. “Becoming well-informed about the disease is one important long-term strategy.”\r\nApart from this, the doctor prescribes good coping skills, a strong support network and respite care to help caregivers handle the stress of caring for a loved one with Alzheimer’s disease.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2507" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2507" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Image-4-2-300x223.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="223" /> US consul General, His Excellency Peter Haas giving the award of OutStanding Achiever to Dr. Shreepad Khedekar[/caption]\r\n<h2>What homeopathy costs?</h2>\r\nYour first consultation with a private homeopath will usually cost between INR 500 to INR 10,000. Further appointments usually cost less – about INR 500 to INR 5000 depending on the location of the place and experience of homeopath. It will also depend on the skill level of his staff or assistants who usually take the first case and prepare it for the main consultant.\r\n\r\nYour remedy will usually be included in the consultation price, but do check this first. Homeopathic tablets or other products usually cost around INR 100 to INR500 if you need to buy them separately in India.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2341" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2341" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DR.-KHEDEKAR.-KHEDEKAR-300x167.png" alt="" width="300" height="167" /> Imperial clinics Mumbai[/caption]\r\n\r\n<b><a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar, BHMS, MD</a> (homeopathy), a specialist for over 17 years, he has used homeopathy in his Switzerland, Belgrade and Mumbai practice for the last 17 years. He lectures in homeopathy at Switzerland, Croatia and at the Serbian Doctors Association (SLD) Teaching Centre in Belgrade and has a busy private practice in Dadar, Mumbai and at Shushrusha Citizens co-operative hospital, Mumbai and is the only Homeopath in their 60 year history.</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Dr. <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Shreepad</a> <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Khedekar</a>  is the Clinical Director, Imperial clinics Mumbai and Imperial clinics Belgrade, Consultant at Shushrusha Citizens Co-op Hospital Mumbai and Physician to several international stars and celebrities.</b>\r\n\r\nPlease do take a look at his CV: <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Can homeopathy help those with Alzheimer’s Disease?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '77-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-08-11 09:56:12', '2017-08-11 09:56:12', '', 77, 'http://eheilung.com/ehblog/?p=78', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(79, 1, '2017-08-11 09:58:29', '2017-08-11 09:58:29', '<strong>What makes the internationally famous celebrities, the rich and famous (movers and shakers) real fans of Homeopathy treatment?</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Their existing doctors of modern medicine/allopathy/classic medicine have failed to give them the desired or promised results</li>\r\n 	<li>Their problems are recurring in spite of having spent millions of dollars on their ailments and having taken treatment from the biggest institutes, clinics and hospitals</li>\r\n 	<li>Side effects of conventional treatments are huge and have only complicated matters for them</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy is safe and secure</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy has no side effects</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy offers sure and permanent results</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy is harmless</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy understands the patient as a whole</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy understands the real problem that comes from physical and mental stress</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy cures from the root</li>\r\n 	<li>They are interested in wholistic and spiritual healing</li>\r\n 	<li>They don''t look at quick fixes and short term gains or suppressions for their problems</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>So what is Homeopathy: </strong>\r\n\r\nHomeopathy was founded by the German physician <b>Samuel Hahnemann</b> (1755-1843), who was much disturbed by the medical system of his time, believing that its cures were crude and some of its strong drugs and treatments did more harm than good to patients. Hahnemann performed experiments on himself using Peruvian bark, which contains quinine, a malaria<b> </b>remedy. He concluded that in a healthy person, quinine creates the same symptoms as malaria, including fevers and chills , which is the reason why it is effective as a remedy. He then began to analyze the remedies available in nature by what he called provings. Provings of homeopathic remedies are still compiled by dosing healthy adults with various substances and documenting the results, in terms of the dose needed to produce the symptoms and the length of the dose''s effectiveness. The provings are collected in large homeopathic references called <i>materia medica</i> or materials of medicine.\r\n\r\n<strong>Hahnemann formulated these principles of homeopathy:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Law of Similars (like cures like)</li>\r\n 	<li>Law of the Infinitesimal Dose (The more diluted a remedy is, the more potent it is)</li>\r\n 	<li>Illness is specific to the individual.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHahnemann''s Law of Similars was based on thinking that dated back to <a href="http://www.encyclopedia.com/people/medicine/medicine-biographies/hippocrates" data-topic="1226283">Hippocrates</a> in the fourth century AD\r\n\r\n<strong>Internationally famous Famous People Who Use Homeopathy:</strong>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Queen Elizabeth 2,</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/the-times/queen-uses-homeopathy-for-cold/news-story/ca4735076e60ce2d82ccbf763ac6955d"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2573" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/elizabeth-242x300.png" alt="" width="242" height="300" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/the-times/queen-uses-homeopathy-for-cold/news-story/ca4735076e60ce2d82ccbf763ac6955d">http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/the-times/queen-uses-homeopathy-for-cold/news-story/ca4735076e60ce2d82ccbf763ac6955d</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Charles Darwin (writer and philosopher),</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2816387/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2574" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Darwin.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="191" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2816387/">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2816387/</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">David Beckham (English footballer),</span>\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2576" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Beckham-300x157.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="157" />\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Mahatma Gandhi,</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2575" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/gandhi-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="199" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Rabindranath Tagore (Indian poet and writer),</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.thehindu.com/2000/03/07/stories/13070179.htm"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2577" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Tagore-300x158.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="158" />http://www.thehindu.com/2000/03/07/stories/13070179.htm</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Dr. Charles Menninger (founder of the famous Menninger Clinic),</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://books.google.co.in/books?id=J7oestO-BnAC&amp;pg=PA185&amp;lpg=PA185&amp;dq=menninger+on+homeopathy&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=vg3FMkWlfU&amp;sig=ONBGNNORc7hP4HIzjOkW0sFu9J8&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj8k6SWsNfTAhWHsY8KHWMDA0AQ6AEIRDAH#v=onepage&amp;q=menninger%20on%20homeopathy&amp;f=false"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2578" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Menninger.jpg" alt="" width="172" height="210" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://books.google.co.in/books?id=J7oestO-BnAC&amp;pg=PA185&amp;lpg=PA185&amp;dq=menninger+on+homeopathy&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=vg3FMkWlfU&amp;sig=ONBGNNORc7hP4HIzjOkW0sFu9J8&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj8k6SWsNfTAhWHsY8KHWMDA0AQ6AEIRDAH#v=onepage&amp;q=menninger%20on%20homeopathy&amp;f=false">https://books.google.co.in/books?id=J7oestO-BnAC&amp;pg=PA185&amp;lpg=PA185&amp;dq=menninger+on+homeopathy&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=vg3FMkWlfU&amp;sig=ONBGNNORc7hP4HIzjOkW0sFu9J8&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj8k6SWsNfTAhWHsY8KHWMDA0AQ6AEIRDAH#v=onepage&amp;q=menninger%20on%20homeopathy&amp;f=false</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Dizzie Gillespie </span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Mark Twain,</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Mark_Twain"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2579" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Mark-twain-real-300x141.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="141" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Mark_Twain">http://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Mark_Twain</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Marko Pantelic (European football star),</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2580" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Marko-Pantelic-on-Homeopathy-300x201.png" alt="" width="300" height="201" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Robert Mimran (French industrialist),</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2581" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_1103-225x300.jpeg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Novak Djokovic (current tennis star),</span>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2247" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2247" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/IMG_0008-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /> with Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar at his clinic in Belgrade[/caption]\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Janko Tipsarevic (tennis star),</span>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2034" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2034" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/cv_7-300x226.png" alt="" width="300" height="226" /> Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar treating Janko Tipsarevic[/caption]\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Bishop David (orthodox catholic head),</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2582" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/david-bishop-208x300.jpg" alt="" width="208" height="300" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Lepa Brena (European pop star),</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2583" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Brena-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Slobodan Zivojinovic (wimbledon star)</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><strong>Some interesting quotes:</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">“No individual has done more good to the medical profession than Samuel Hahnemann (the father of homeopathy).” He added: </span><span class="home15gray">“I can''t remember a time when I didn''t want to be a doctor. The doctors I knew as a very young child must have helped to plant the desire in me, when I was as young as five or six. One Homeopathic physician, Dr. Justice Gage Wright, was a great model.”\r\n–C. Everett Koop, M.D. (Surgeon General of the United States from 1982-1989)\r\n</span><span class="footnotes">Published in <em>Koop</em>, New York: Harper, 1992.</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2586" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Koop-300x169.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="169" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">John D. Rockefeller lived to the ripe old age of 98 and was known to have his homeopath often travel with him. He said that homeopathy is “a progressive and aggressive step in medicine.”</span>\r\n<h2><strong><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2587" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Rockefeller-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Adolf Hitler was one of the most ardent supporters of Homeopathy from 1920 till he died in 1945. He supported homeopathy because it helped him and the science was German in origin. He was single handedly responsible for reviving homeopathy after the first World War. </strong></h2>\r\n<strong><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2568" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/hitler-300x169.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="169" /></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Other famous people in support of Homeopathy:</strong>\r\n\r\nOther famous people who have been known to use homeopathic medicines include Charles Dickens, W.B. Yeats, William Thackeray, Benjamin Disraeli, Pope Pius X, Louisa May Alcott, Susan B. Anthony, William Lloyd Garrison, Daniel Webster, Harriet Beecher Stowe, Henry Wadsworth Longfellow, William Seward, artist Jackson Pollock, W.C. Fields, and former American Presidents James Garfield and William McKinley.\r\n\r\n<strong>Todays Stars:</strong>\r\n\r\nOther modern-day famous people who have publicly declared their interest in and support for homeopathic medicine include: Catherine Zeta-Jones, Whoopi Goldberg, Pamela Anderson, Jane Fonda, Cher, Rosie O''Donnell, Martin Sheen, the Chili Peppers, Jane Seymour, Lesley Anne Warren, Axl Rose, Linda Gray, Susan Blakely, Michael Franks, Cybil Sheppard, Vidal Sassoon, Angelica Houston, Boris Becker, Martina Navratilova, Priscilla and Lisa Marie Presley, Cliff Robertson, Jerry Hall, Diane von Furstenberg, Ashley Judd, Naomi Judd, Olivia Newton-John, Juliana Margulies, JD Salinger, Blythe Danner, Pat Riley (coach of the Miami Heat), and former Prime Minister of England Tony Blair.\r\n\r\n<strong>Famous Homeopathic Quotes</strong>\r\n\r\n“If I was not an actress, I would be a homeopathic doctor”\r\n– Lindsay Wagner\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2588" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Paul_McCartney-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n“I can''t manage without homeopathy. I never go anywhere without homeopathic remedies. I use them often”...\r\n– Paul McCartney\r\n\r\n“It satisfies the therapeutic demands of this age better than any other system or school of medicine.” ...\r\n– Charles Menninger, M.D\r\n\r\n“The introduction of homeopathy forced the old school doctor to stir around and learn something of a rational nature about his business. You may honestly feel grateful that homeopathy survived the attempts of allopaths (the orthodox physicians) to destroy it.”\r\n– Mark Twain\r\n\r\n“There have been two great revelations in my life: The first was bepop, the second was homeopathy.”\r\n– Dizzy Gillespie, great jazz musician\r\n\r\n“Effective natural remedies that have no side effects.”\r\n– Robert Mendelsohn, M.D., Professor, University of Illinois Medical School and best-selling author\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2589" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Menuhin-300x141.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="141" />\r\n\r\n“Homeopathy is the safest and most reliable approach to ailments and has withstood the assaults of established medical practice for over 100 years.”\r\n– Yehudi Menuhin, world famous violinist\r\n\r\nHillary Rodham Clinton has been known to send homeopathic remedies to her colleagues.\r\n\r\n<strong>Many of the above have been Dr. Khedekar''s patients.</strong>\r\n\r\nHomeopathy has survived for centuries because serious intellectuals, successful people, celebrities, billionaires, heads of state, great sportsmen and supreme athletes have endorsed it wholeheartedly.\r\n\r\nRecently Dr. Shreepad Khedekar  (undoubtedly the best homeopath in the world) was called upon by a billionaire in St. Tropez, France for health issues of the entire family. It definitely was an overwhelming feeling for a true propagator of this wonderful science of Homeopathy! Coming from a country like India this was a great honour for him to be called upon at this fancy place to treat them. <strong>He makes the Indian system of homeopathy proud!</strong>\r\n\r\nBelow are some breath taking pictures of their lifestyle:\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2537" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2537" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5845-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /> <strong><img class="size-medium wp-image-2561" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6071-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></strong>[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2560" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6067-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2559" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6057-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2558" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6033-e1493929992612-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2543" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5912-e1493930152490-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2554" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5998-e1493930053746-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2553" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5985-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2555" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6004-e1493930024409-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2556" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6026-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2557" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_110a-300x300.jpeg" alt="" width="300" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2552" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_1108-300x225.jpeg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2551" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_110b-300x225.jpeg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\nBatman\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2547" align="alignnone" width="225"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2547" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_1109-225x300.jpeg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /> St. Tropez, Club 55<img class="size-medium wp-image-2546" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5944-e1493930117268-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2545" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5925-e1493930182963-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\nDr. Shreepad A. Khedekar. Khedekar, Homeopath to the rich and famous billionaires\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2544" align="alignnone" width="225"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2544" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_110d-225x300.jpeg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /> Curing patients at the pool side in style<img class="size-medium wp-image-2541" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5905-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2540" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5888-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\nDr. Khedekar, Homeopath to the rich and famous billionaires\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2539" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2539" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6097-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /> Homeopath to the rich and famous billionaires[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2538" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5848-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2537" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2537" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5845-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /> Homeopath to the rich and famous billionaires[/caption]\r\n<h2>What homeopathy costs?</h2>\r\nYour first consultation with a private homeopath will usually cost between INR 500 to INR 10,000. Further appointments usually cost less – about INR 500 to INR 5000 depending on the location of the place and experience of homeopath. It will also depend on the skill level of his staff or assistants who usually take the first case and prepare it for the main consultant.\r\n\r\nYour remedy will usually be included in the consultation price, but do check this first. Homeopathic tablets or other products usually cost around INR 100 to INR500 if you need to buy them separately in India.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2341" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2341" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DR.-KHEDEKAR.-KHEDEKAR-300x167.png" alt="" width="300" height="167" /> Imperial clinics Mumbai[/caption]\r\n\r\n<b><a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar, BHMS, MD</a> (homeopathy), a specialist for over 17 years, he has used homeopathy in his Switzerland, Belgrade and Mumbai practice for the last 17 years. He lectures in homeopathy at Switzerland, Croatia and at the Serbian Doctors Association (SLD) Teaching Centre in Belgrade and has a busy private practice in Dadar, Mumbai and at Shushrusha Citizens co-operative hospital, Mumbai and is the only Homeopath in their 60 year history.</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Dr. <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Shreepad</a> <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Khedekar</a>  is the Clinical Director, Imperial clinics Mumbai and Imperial clinics Belgrade, Consultant at Shushrusha Citizens Co-op Hospital Mumbai and Physician to several international stars and celebrities.</b>\r\n\r\nPlease do take a look at his CV: <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Or email your question on imperialclinics@gmail.com</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Why do Powerful people take Homeopathy treatment?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why-do-powerful-people-take-homeopathy-treatment', '', '', '2017-08-11 09:58:29', '2017-08-11 09:58:29', '', 0, 'http://eheilung.com/ehblog/?p=79', 0, 'post', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(81, 1, '2017-08-11 09:58:29', '2017-08-11 09:58:29', '<strong>What makes the internationally famous celebrities, the rich and famous (movers and shakers) real fans of Homeopathy treatment?</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Their existing doctors of modern medicine/allopathy/classic medicine have failed to give them the desired or promised results</li>\r\n 	<li>Their problems are recurring in spite of having spent millions of dollars on their ailments and having taken treatment from the biggest institutes, clinics and hospitals</li>\r\n 	<li>Side effects of conventional treatments are huge and have only complicated matters for them</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy is safe and secure</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy has no side effects</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy offers sure and permanent results</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy is harmless</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy understands the patient as a whole</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy understands the real problem that comes from physical and mental stress</li>\r\n 	<li>Homeopathy cures from the root</li>\r\n 	<li>They are interested in wholistic and spiritual healing</li>\r\n 	<li>They don''t look at quick fixes and short term gains or suppressions for their problems</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>So what is Homeopathy: </strong>\r\n\r\nHomeopathy was founded by the German physician <b>Samuel Hahnemann</b> (1755-1843), who was much disturbed by the medical system of his time, believing that its cures were crude and some of its strong drugs and treatments did more harm than good to patients. Hahnemann performed experiments on himself using Peruvian bark, which contains quinine, a malaria<b> </b>remedy. He concluded that in a healthy person, quinine creates the same symptoms as malaria, including fevers and chills , which is the reason why it is effective as a remedy. He then began to analyze the remedies available in nature by what he called provings. Provings of homeopathic remedies are still compiled by dosing healthy adults with various substances and documenting the results, in terms of the dose needed to produce the symptoms and the length of the dose''s effectiveness. The provings are collected in large homeopathic references called <i>materia medica</i> or materials of medicine.\r\n\r\n<strong>Hahnemann formulated these principles of homeopathy:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Law of Similars (like cures like)</li>\r\n 	<li>Law of the Infinitesimal Dose (The more diluted a remedy is, the more potent it is)</li>\r\n 	<li>Illness is specific to the individual.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHahnemann''s Law of Similars was based on thinking that dated back to <a href="http://www.encyclopedia.com/people/medicine/medicine-biographies/hippocrates" data-topic="1226283">Hippocrates</a> in the fourth century AD\r\n\r\n<strong>Internationally famous Famous People Who Use Homeopathy:</strong>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Queen Elizabeth 2,</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/the-times/queen-uses-homeopathy-for-cold/news-story/ca4735076e60ce2d82ccbf763ac6955d"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2573" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/elizabeth-242x300.png" alt="" width="242" height="300" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/the-times/queen-uses-homeopathy-for-cold/news-story/ca4735076e60ce2d82ccbf763ac6955d">http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/the-times/queen-uses-homeopathy-for-cold/news-story/ca4735076e60ce2d82ccbf763ac6955d</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Charles Darwin (writer and philosopher),</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2816387/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2574" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Darwin.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="191" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2816387/">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2816387/</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">David Beckham (English footballer),</span>\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2576" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Beckham-300x157.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="157" />\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Mahatma Gandhi,</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2575" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/gandhi-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="199" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Rabindranath Tagore (Indian poet and writer),</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.thehindu.com/2000/03/07/stories/13070179.htm"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2577" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Tagore-300x158.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="158" />http://www.thehindu.com/2000/03/07/stories/13070179.htm</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Dr. Charles Menninger (founder of the famous Menninger Clinic),</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://books.google.co.in/books?id=J7oestO-BnAC&amp;pg=PA185&amp;lpg=PA185&amp;dq=menninger+on+homeopathy&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=vg3FMkWlfU&amp;sig=ONBGNNORc7hP4HIzjOkW0sFu9J8&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj8k6SWsNfTAhWHsY8KHWMDA0AQ6AEIRDAH#v=onepage&amp;q=menninger%20on%20homeopathy&amp;f=false"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2578" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Menninger.jpg" alt="" width="172" height="210" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://books.google.co.in/books?id=J7oestO-BnAC&amp;pg=PA185&amp;lpg=PA185&amp;dq=menninger+on+homeopathy&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=vg3FMkWlfU&amp;sig=ONBGNNORc7hP4HIzjOkW0sFu9J8&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj8k6SWsNfTAhWHsY8KHWMDA0AQ6AEIRDAH#v=onepage&amp;q=menninger%20on%20homeopathy&amp;f=false">https://books.google.co.in/books?id=J7oestO-BnAC&amp;pg=PA185&amp;lpg=PA185&amp;dq=menninger+on+homeopathy&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=vg3FMkWlfU&amp;sig=ONBGNNORc7hP4HIzjOkW0sFu9J8&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj8k6SWsNfTAhWHsY8KHWMDA0AQ6AEIRDAH#v=onepage&amp;q=menninger%20on%20homeopathy&amp;f=false</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Dizzie Gillespie </span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Mark Twain,</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Mark_Twain"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2579" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Mark-twain-real-300x141.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="141" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Mark_Twain">http://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Mark_Twain</a>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Marko Pantelic (European football star),</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2580" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Marko-Pantelic-on-Homeopathy-300x201.png" alt="" width="300" height="201" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Robert Mimran (French industrialist),</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2581" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_1103-225x300.jpeg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Novak Djokovic (current tennis star),</span>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2247" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2247" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/IMG_0008-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /> with Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar at his clinic in Belgrade[/caption]\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Janko Tipsarevic (tennis star),</span>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2034" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2034" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/cv_7-300x226.png" alt="" width="300" height="226" /> Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar treating Janko Tipsarevic[/caption]\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Bishop David (orthodox catholic head),</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2582" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/david-bishop-208x300.jpg" alt="" width="208" height="300" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Lepa Brena (European pop star),</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2583" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Brena-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">Slobodan Zivojinovic (wimbledon star)</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><strong>Some interesting quotes:</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">“No individual has done more good to the medical profession than Samuel Hahnemann (the father of homeopathy).” He added: </span><span class="home15gray">“I can''t remember a time when I didn''t want to be a doctor. The doctors I knew as a very young child must have helped to plant the desire in me, when I was as young as five or six. One Homeopathic physician, Dr. Justice Gage Wright, was a great model.”\r\n–C. Everett Koop, M.D. (Surgeon General of the United States from 1982-1989)\r\n</span><span class="footnotes">Published in <em>Koop</em>, New York: Harper, 1992.</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2586" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Koop-300x169.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="169" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span class="home15gray">John D. Rockefeller lived to the ripe old age of 98 and was known to have his homeopath often travel with him. He said that homeopathy is “a progressive and aggressive step in medicine.”</span>\r\n<h2><strong><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2587" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Rockefeller-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Adolf Hitler was one of the most ardent supporters of Homeopathy from 1920 till he died in 1945. He supported homeopathy because it helped him and the science was German in origin. He was single handedly responsible for reviving homeopathy after the first World War. </strong></h2>\r\n<strong><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2568" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/hitler-300x169.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="169" /></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Other famous people in support of Homeopathy:</strong>\r\n\r\nOther famous people who have been known to use homeopathic medicines include Charles Dickens, W.B. Yeats, William Thackeray, Benjamin Disraeli, Pope Pius X, Louisa May Alcott, Susan B. Anthony, William Lloyd Garrison, Daniel Webster, Harriet Beecher Stowe, Henry Wadsworth Longfellow, William Seward, artist Jackson Pollock, W.C. Fields, and former American Presidents James Garfield and William McKinley.\r\n\r\n<strong>Todays Stars:</strong>\r\n\r\nOther modern-day famous people who have publicly declared their interest in and support for homeopathic medicine include: Catherine Zeta-Jones, Whoopi Goldberg, Pamela Anderson, Jane Fonda, Cher, Rosie O''Donnell, Martin Sheen, the Chili Peppers, Jane Seymour, Lesley Anne Warren, Axl Rose, Linda Gray, Susan Blakely, Michael Franks, Cybil Sheppard, Vidal Sassoon, Angelica Houston, Boris Becker, Martina Navratilova, Priscilla and Lisa Marie Presley, Cliff Robertson, Jerry Hall, Diane von Furstenberg, Ashley Judd, Naomi Judd, Olivia Newton-John, Juliana Margulies, JD Salinger, Blythe Danner, Pat Riley (coach of the Miami Heat), and former Prime Minister of England Tony Blair.\r\n\r\n<strong>Famous Homeopathic Quotes</strong>\r\n\r\n“If I was not an actress, I would be a homeopathic doctor”\r\n– Lindsay Wagner\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2588" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Paul_McCartney-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n“I can''t manage without homeopathy. I never go anywhere without homeopathic remedies. I use them often”...\r\n– Paul McCartney\r\n\r\n“It satisfies the therapeutic demands of this age better than any other system or school of medicine.” ...\r\n– Charles Menninger, M.D\r\n\r\n“The introduction of homeopathy forced the old school doctor to stir around and learn something of a rational nature about his business. You may honestly feel grateful that homeopathy survived the attempts of allopaths (the orthodox physicians) to destroy it.”\r\n– Mark Twain\r\n\r\n“There have been two great revelations in my life: The first was bepop, the second was homeopathy.”\r\n– Dizzy Gillespie, great jazz musician\r\n\r\n“Effective natural remedies that have no side effects.”\r\n– Robert Mendelsohn, M.D., Professor, University of Illinois Medical School and best-selling author\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2589" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Menuhin-300x141.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="141" />\r\n\r\n“Homeopathy is the safest and most reliable approach to ailments and has withstood the assaults of established medical practice for over 100 years.”\r\n– Yehudi Menuhin, world famous violinist\r\n\r\nHillary Rodham Clinton has been known to send homeopathic remedies to her colleagues.\r\n\r\n<strong>Many of the above have been Dr. Khedekar''s patients.</strong>\r\n\r\nHomeopathy has survived for centuries because serious intellectuals, successful people, celebrities, billionaires, heads of state, great sportsmen and supreme athletes have endorsed it wholeheartedly.\r\n\r\nRecently Dr. Shreepad Khedekar  (undoubtedly the best homeopath in the world) was called upon by a billionaire in St. Tropez, France for health issues of the entire family. It definitely was an overwhelming feeling for a true propagator of this wonderful science of Homeopathy! Coming from a country like India this was a great honour for him to be called upon at this fancy place to treat them. <strong>He makes the Indian system of homeopathy proud!</strong>\r\n\r\nBelow are some breath taking pictures of their lifestyle:\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2537" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2537" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5845-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /> <strong><img class="size-medium wp-image-2561" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6071-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></strong>[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2560" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6067-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2559" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6057-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2558" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6033-e1493929992612-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2543" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5912-e1493930152490-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2554" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5998-e1493930053746-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2553" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5985-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2555" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6004-e1493930024409-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2556" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6026-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2557" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_110a-300x300.jpeg" alt="" width="300" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2552" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_1108-300x225.jpeg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2551" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_110b-300x225.jpeg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\nBatman\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2547" align="alignnone" width="225"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2547" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_1109-225x300.jpeg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /> St. Tropez, Club 55<img class="size-medium wp-image-2546" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5944-e1493930117268-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2545" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5925-e1493930182963-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" />\r\n\r\nDr. Shreepad A. Khedekar. Khedekar, Homeopath to the rich and famous billionaires\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2544" align="alignnone" width="225"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2544" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fullsizeoutput_110d-225x300.jpeg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /> Curing patients at the pool side in style<img class="size-medium wp-image-2541" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5905-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2540" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5888-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\nDr. Khedekar, Homeopath to the rich and famous billionaires\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2539" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2539" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_6097-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /> Homeopath to the rich and famous billionaires[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2538" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5848-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2537" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2537" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5845-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /> Homeopath to the rich and famous billionaires[/caption]\r\n<h2>What homeopathy costs?</h2>\r\nYour first consultation with a private homeopath will usually cost between INR 500 to INR 10,000. Further appointments usually cost less – about INR 500 to INR 5000 depending on the location of the place and experience of homeopath. It will also depend on the skill level of his staff or assistants who usually take the first case and prepare it for the main consultant.\r\n\r\nYour remedy will usually be included in the consultation price, but do check this first. Homeopathic tablets or other products usually cost around INR 100 to INR500 if you need to buy them separately in India.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_2341" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-2341" src="http://imperialclinics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DR.-KHEDEKAR.-KHEDEKAR-300x167.png" alt="" width="300" height="167" /> Imperial clinics Mumbai[/caption]\r\n\r\n<b><a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Dr. Shreepad A. Khedekar, BHMS, MD</a> (homeopathy), a specialist for over 17 years, he has used homeopathy in his Switzerland, Belgrade and Mumbai practice for the last 17 years. He lectures in homeopathy at Switzerland, Croatia and at the Serbian Doctors Association (SLD) Teaching Centre in Belgrade and has a busy private practice in Dadar, Mumbai and at Shushrusha Citizens co-operative hospital, Mumbai and is the only Homeopath in their 60 year history.</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Dr. <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Shreepad</a> <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">Khedekar</a>  is the Clinical Director, Imperial clinics Mumbai and Imperial clinics Belgrade, Consultant at Shushrusha Citizens Co-op Hospital Mumbai and Physician to several international stars and celebrities.</b>\r\n\r\nPlease do take a look at his CV: <a href="http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum">http://imperialclinics.com/dr-shreepad-khedekar-imperial-clinics-autism-spectrum</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Or email your question on imperialclinics@gmail.com</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Why do Powerful people take Homeopathy treatment?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '79-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-08-11 09:58:29', '2017-08-11 09:58:29', '', 79, 'http://eheilung.com/ehblog/?p=81', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
